Money Stuff =0A Programming note: Money Stuff will be off tomorrow and earl=
y next week, back =0AWednesday, Dec. 11.Here=E2=80=99s the basic idea of co=
nvertible arbitra =0A=0A=0A =0A<https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/authors/A=
RbTQlRLRjE/matthew-s-levine=3Fcmpid=3DBBD120524_MONEYSTUFF&utm_medium=3Dema=
il&utm_source=3Dnewsletter&utm_term=3D241205&utm_campaign=3Dmoneystuff>=0A =
