32&m=3D21d6dea82d6b16615cf44233be620525&p=3D12052024>=0A=0A=0AProgramming n=
ote: Money Stuff will be off tomorrow and early next week, back =0AWednesda=
y, Dec. 11.=0A=0A=0AMicroStrategy=0A=0AHere=E2=80=99s the basic idea of con=
vertible arbitrage. You buy a convertible bond =0Athat will pay you back, i=
n a year, either (1) $1,000 in cash or (2) 20 shares =0Aof the company=E2=
=80=99s stock. (Or some other =E2=80=9Cconversion ratio=E2=80=9D; 20 is an =
